\c 65
\s Dhavhidhi anorumbidza Mwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba. Pisarema Rwiyo rwaDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Imi Mwari munofanira kurumbidzwa paZioni; Imi munofanira kuitirwa mhiko.
\v 2 Imi vokunzwa munyengetero, Vanhu vose vanofanira kuuya kwamuri.
\v 3 Mashoko akaipa ondikunda; Kana kuri kudarika kwedu muchakudzima imi.
\v 4 Akaropafadzwa munhu wamunosanangura, wamunoswededza kwamuri, Kuti agare pavazhe dzenyu; Isu tichagutiswa nounaki hweimba yenyu, Iyo nzvimbo tsvene yetemberi yenyu.
\v 5 Mukururama kwenyu munotipindura nezvinhu zvinotyisa, Imi Mwari muponesi wedu; Imi chivimbo chamativi ose apasi, Navari kure pagungwa;
\v 6 Iye, anoteya makomo nesimba rake; Iye, akasungwa chiuno nesimba;
\v 7 Iye, unonyaradza kutinhira kwamakungwa,
\s iko kutinhira kwamafungo awo, Nokupopota kwavanhu.
\p
\v 8 Naivo vagere kumigumo vanotya zviratidzo zvenyu;
\s Munofadza mabudiro amangwanani naamadeko.
\p
\v 9 Munoshanyira pasi, munopadiridza, Munopafumisa kwazvo;
\s Rwizi rwaMwari ruzere nemvura; Munovagadzirira zviyo, kana magadzira pasi saizvozvo.
\s IÂ° Munozadza mihoronp yapo
\s kwazvo;
\s Munoenzanisa mipanje yapo; Munopanyorovesa nemvura inopfunha;
\s Munoropafadza zvinomera zvapo. uMunoshongedza mwaka nekorona younaki hwenyu;
\s Makwara enyu anodonha mafuta.
\p
\v 12 Anodonha pamafuro erenje; Zvikomo zvinozvisunga nomufaro.
\p
\v 13 Mafuro akafukidzwa namapoka ezvipfuwo;
\s Uye mipatawo yakafukidzwa nezviyo;
\s Zvinopururudza, zvichiimbawo.
